  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">uo</span> počinje sa jezikom postavljenim na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>, dok su usne savijene i potisnute napred. Zatim, bez prekidanja zvuka, smirili smo jezik i malo spuštali vrat ka poziciji <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span>.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">uo</span> je praćen početnim konsonantima, dobija slogove kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">duo</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tuo</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">guo</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">zhuo</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">shuo</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite ove slogove, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">guo</span> u različitim tonovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Slova</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">guō</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">锅</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">guó</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">国</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">guǒ</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">果</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">guò</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">过</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
